Usage: set_opt_slack_weighting_factor [-help] <factor> [-hold] [-setup]
                                      -view <string>

-help              # Prints out the command usage
<factor>           # slack weighting factor (float, required)
-hold              # apply factor to hold (bool, optional)
-setup             # apply factor to setup (bool, optional)
-view <string>     # view for which slack weights are defined
                   # (string, required)